<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西继续听地下传来的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到地在动的声音。”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地下好像有一台大机器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又听到那些说话的声音了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们是从哪里来的呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看着史密斯侦探和建筑工人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有人，都往后退！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西像一只陀螺一样开始旋转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脚下出现一个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沥青块飞得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她越转越快，以极快的速度钻进地下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”史密斯侦探叫道，“你在干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，罗西没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经到了很深的地下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西来到一个巨大的黑洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！有一个人类！”轰鸣声中一个声音大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑暗中，罗西用她的超级视力，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到几个小矮人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们长着鼹鼠的脸，穿着棕色的工作服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些人站在一台大机器旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器看上去像是用卡车零件和其他建筑设备组装的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是谁？”罗西生气地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一个男人拉了一下操作杆，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器停止了运作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是鼹鼠人！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们打算毁了美罗城！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。“你们为什么要那么做？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠人生气地看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们讨厌人类在这里挖下水道和地铁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地下只能是我们鼹鼠人的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着其他鼹鼠人，“抓住她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个鼹鼠人跑向罗西，向她挥动着铁管。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳着躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠人撞到洞穴的墙壁上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！”其中一个喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！另一个鼹鼠人挥动着铁管。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎哟！”第一个鼹鼠人又叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”另一个鼹鼠人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个鼹鼠人看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她去哪里了？”他们问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些鼹鼠人看不太清楚。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像真正的鼹鼠一样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在那里！”一个鼹鼠人指着罗西说，“抓住她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更多的鼹鼠人向罗西跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地下不能有人类！”一个鼹鼠人大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地下只能是鼹鼠人的！”第二个鼹鼠人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西再一次跳着躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的鼹鼠人撞在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们被绊倒，撞在了墙上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个鼹鼠人仍然站在地震机器前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拉下操作杆，机器发出吵闹的轰鸣声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！机器发射出一道强烈的光线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光线炸毁了洞穴的顶部，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一块块大石头向罗西砸下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>